	* PeterThoeny - 26 Oct 1998: Added revision control using RCS. Each topic has now a list of revisions at the bottom and a revision info, e.g. <br> <code> Topic <nop>TWikiHistory . { Edit | Ref-By | r1.3 | r1.2 | r1.1 } <br> Revision r1.3: 1998/10/26 01:34:00 by PeterThoeny </code>
